<div type="textpart" subtype="argumentum">
<head rend="red rustic-caps">
<lb/><expan>in<abbr rend="supraline">cip</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <expan><abbr rend="supraline">arg</abbr><ex>umentum</ex></expan> ad <name>thimothe<expan><abbr rend="supraline">u</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan></name>
</head>
<p rend="rustic-caps">
<lb/>Inpriinis dicendum est cur apostolus <name>paulus</name> in hac epistula scri- bendo non seruauerit morem suum ut uel uocabulum nominis sui uel ordinis scriberet dignitatem. <name>haec</name> causa est quod ad eos scribens qui ex circumcisione crediderant quasi gentium apostolus et non <name>haebraeo</name>- rum sciens quocpie eorum superbiam suamque humilitatem ipse demonstrans meritum officii sui noluit anteferre. <name>nam</name> simili modo iam lo- hannes apostolus propter humilitatem in epistula sua nomen suum eadem ratione non praetulit. <name>hanc</name> ergo epistulam fertur apostolus ad ” <name>hebraeos</name> conscriptam haebraica lingua misisse: cuius sensum et ordinem retinens Lucas euangelista post excessum beati apostoli graeco sermone conscripsit.    
</p>
<div type="textpart" subtype="finalRubric">
<p rend="red rustic-caps">
<lb/><expan><expan>e<abbr rend="supraline">xp</abbr><ex>licit</ex></expan></expan> <expan>a<abbr rend="supraline">ag</abbr><ex>umentum</ex></expan> 
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div type="textpart" subtype="capitula">
<list>
<head rend="red rustic-caps">
<lb/>Incipiunt capitula
</head>
<lb/><item><label>i</label> Senior <name>gaio</name> carissimo scribit 
<lb rend="indent"/>gaudens de aduentu fratrum 
<lb rend="indent"/>et audiens eum ueritatem 
<lb rend="indent"/>custodire</item>
<lb/><item><label>ii</label> Quod fideliter ope<add place="above">ra</add>retur in pere
<lb break="no"/>grinis et testimonium de eo 
<lb rend="indent"/>reddentes</item>
<lb/><item><label>iii</label> Scribit de <name>diotre<subst><del rend="alt">r</del><add place="inline">p</add><add place="above">h</add></subst>es</name> quod non reci
<lb break="no"/>peret doctrina eius sed et eos 
<lb rend="indent"/>qui cupiunt doctrina eius 
<lb rend="indent"/>de ecclesia eicit</item>
<lb/><item><label>iiii</label> Qui bene facit ex <name><expan>d<ex>e</ex><abbr rend="supraline">o</abbr></expan></name> est et <name>demetrio</name> 
<lb rend="indent"/>testimonium redditur</item>
<lb/><item><label>v</label> Nolui multa scribere tibi <add place="inRas">sperans</add> 
<lb rend="indent"/>protinus te uidere<reg>.</reg> <quote>salutant te amici</quote><surplus>:~</surplus></item>
</list>
<div type="textpart" subtype="finalRubric">
<p rend="red rustic-caps">
<lb/>expliciunt capitula
</p>
